## Deploy Scripts

### Deploy Web

```bash
# scripts/deploy-web.sh
#!/bin/bash

ENV=$1

if [ "$ENV" == "pro" ]; then
  echo "Deploying to PRODUCTION"
  aws s3 sync www/ s3://asyb-prod-website --delete
  aws cloudfront create-invalidation --distribution-id EXXXXX --paths "/*"
elif [ "$ENV" == "pre" ]; then
  echo "Deploying to PREPRODUCTION"
  aws s3 sync www/ s3://asyb-pre-website --delete
fi

echo "✅ Deploy completed"
```

